
'''''Platoon Leader''''' ni film ya Cannon Films yo mu 1988 yakozwe mu ntambara ya Vietnam kandi iyobowe na Aaron Norris<ref>Platoon Leader (1988) | Radio Times <nowiki>https://www.radiotimes.com</nowiki> › movie-guide › platoon-le...</ref>; ikinamo Michael Dudikoff na Michael DeLorenzo kandi yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo. Rishingiye ku nyandiko ya James R. McDonough yibuka izina rimwe<ref>Platoon Leader (film) - Academic Dictionaries and ... <nowiki>https://en-academic.com</nowiki> › dic.nsf › enwiki</ref>. Iyi filime ivuga kubyerekeranye na liyetona mushya [[Viyetinamu|w’abasirikare bageze muri Vietnam]] kugira ngo yigarurire platoni ye ya mbere<ref>Platoon | Plot, Cast, Awards, & Facts | Britannica <nowiki>https://www.britannica.com</nowiki> › ... › Movies</ref>. Asanga agomba kwigaragaza no kugirirwa ikizere nabagabo banditswe niba ashaka kubayobora<ref>MOVIE REVIEWS : 'Platoon Leader' Ambushed by Its Own ... <nowiki>https://www.latimes.com</nowiki> › archives › la-xpm-1988-10-...</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Lt. Jeffrey Knight, umusirikare mushya wo mu Ishuri rya Gisirikare rya Leta zunze ubumwe za [[Amerika]],<ref>Is 'Platoon Leader' on Netflix? Where to Watch the Movie <nowiki>https://usa.newonnetflix.info</nowiki> › info</ref> yajyanywe mu ndege ku birindiro biri muri Vietnam, aho ahurira na platon  ye, itsinda ry’abasirikare bakomeye b'intambara<ref>Scene of the Week: Platoon Leader - BULLETPROOF ACTION <nowiki>https://www.bulletproofaction.com</nowiki> › 2018/11/11 › scen...</ref>. Platon Serija McNamara asobanurira Knight ko platoni idakeneye umuyobozi ukurikiza amategeko. Ibikorwa bya Lt. Knight nabyo byamaganwa nabagabo be bose usibye Pvt. Parker, umukoresha wa radio<ref>platoon leader movie review - Farima Joya <nowiki>https://farimajoya.com</nowiki> › platoon-leader-movie-review-...</ref>.

Kuri rimwe mu irondo rye rya mbere, Knight yasitaye atitaye ku kirombe cyanjye cy'urugendo kandi aricwa. Parker noneho amaradiyo ya evac hanyuma McNamara ategeka ingabo kwimukira muri LZ kugirango zivemo<ref>Platoon Leader - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › platoon_leader</ref> . Nyuma, mu gihe Lt. Knight arimo gukira ibikomere mu bitaro bya Gisirikare, Major Flynn amubaza niba ashobora kongera gufata icyemezo maze Knight arabyemera<ref>Watch Platoon Leader (1988) Full Movie Online Free <nowiki>https://www.123movie.lc</nowiki> › Movies</ref>. Knight asubizwa mu ndege asubira ku birindiro bya platon ariko ntiyakirwa n'abantu be asanga ibikoresho bye byabuze aho yari atuye, kuko batari biteze ko azagaruka<ref>Platoon Leader (1988) - Turner Classic Movies - TCM <nowiki>https://www.tcm.com</nowiki> › tcmdb › title › platoon-leader</ref>. Bamenye ko Knight yagarutse, abasirikare bihutira gusubiza ibintu bye hanze y'ibiro bye mbere yuko agaruka. Knight amenya ko agomba gufata ubundi buryo kugirango abagabo be bamwubahe<ref>Platoon Leader (1988) - IMDb <nowiki>https://www.imdb.com</nowiki> › title</ref>.

